snippet.title: PSX Longplay [107] Mr Driller
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played By: ScHlAuChi

A really great action puzzler by Namco!
The first part shows a round of Survival Mode - i kill myself when a depth of 50000 is reached. The second part from 50:20 onwards shows a playthrough of the story mode on expert + ending and credits. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
